OL,5, It's a regular Monday morning in       
OL,6, Ukraine and Fedir Shandor is logging on
OL,7, to conduct his online classes.         
OL,9,FThe university professor has been      
OL,10,Fteaching online since the pandemic but 
OL,11,Ffor the past few months, he has been   
OL,12,Feducating his students from the        
OL,13,Ffrontline.                             
